name: TurtleGeek.com
body: ### ROSTER (Record Of Sea Turtles Electronic Reports) collects marine turtle and holding tank data required by the Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission (FWC). [OUT OF DATE] ### ROSTERWEB (Record Of Sea Turtles Electronic Reports – Web) is the web-based version of ROSTER. [PROOF OF CONCEPT ONLY] ### MANIFEST collects nesting data for Mote Marine Laboratory’s Sea Turtle Conservation and Research Program. [OUT OF DATE] ### TAGFINDER queries Mote Marine Laboratory’s Sea Turtle Conservation and Research Program sea turtle database while in the field. [OUT OF DATE] ### VAQSTAR (Virginia Aquarium Sea Turtle Attribute Repository) collects sea turtle stranding and necropsy data for the Virginia Aquarium and Marine Science Center. [PROOF OF CONCEPT ONLY] ### HANDSTRAND is an Android phone application for collecting sea turtle stranding data. [PROOF OF CONCEPT ONLY] ### Video: Tort and Joie’s video on balloons in the ocean (not cool)
